OL,3,CHouseholds left without water as
OL,4,Cdemand soars in hot weather
OL,6,FHouseholds in a Cornish village and
OL,7,Fsurrounding areas have been left
OL,8,Fwithout water as demand soars during
OL,9,Fthe hot weather.
OL,11,FCustomers in the TR8 and PL27 areas of
OL,12,FSt Eval and surrounding areas have
OL,13,Falready been experiencing low water
OL,14,Fpressure or a temporary loss of supply
OL,15,Ffor more than a week.
OL,17,FResidents have now claimed they were
OL,18,Ftold by South West Water (SWW) that
OL,19,Fthe water supply issues could continue
OL,20,Fin their area until August 9.
