OL,3,CHouseholds left without water as
OL,4,Cdemand soars in hot weather
OL,6,FSouth West Water said: "We are
OL,7,Fcarrying out essential maintenance to
OL,8,Fthe Bears Down service reservoir near
OL,9,FNewquay.
OL,11,F"As demand has also increased due to
OL,12,Fthe recent hot weather, some customers
OL,13,Fhave been experiencing intermittent
OL,14,Fsupply issues, such as low pressure or
OL,15,Fno water during peak periods.
OL,17,F"We have tankers out around the
OL,18,Fnetwork to boost pressure in the area
OL,19,Fand help return supply to normal as we
OL,20,Flook to compete the work as quickly as
OL,21,Fpossible."
