OL,3,CHouseholds left without water as
OL,4,Cdemand soars in hot weather
OL,6,FSWW has not confirmed how long the low
OL,7,Fpressure or water shortages will last.
OL,9,FOne resident first noticed the issues
OL,10,Fon Monday 22 July when the water in
OL,11,Fher home was running a milky colour.
OL,12,FBy Wednesday 24 July, she said the
OL,13,Fwater was coming out brown.
OL,15,FOver the weekend, she said there were
OL,16,Fthree days when she didn't have
OL,17,Frunning water at all and was having to
OL,18,Fuse bottled water to make formula to
OL,19,Ffeed her four-month-old baby.
