OL,3,CHouseholds left without water as
OL,4,Cdemand soars in hot weather
OL,6,FThe Travellers Rest in Trevarrian,
OL,7,Fnear Newquay, has also been left
OL,8,F'devastated' after losing "thousands
OL,9,Fof pounds" in revenue since being left
OL,10,Fwith no running water.
OL,12,FKelly Hill, who runs the pub, said:
OL,13,F"It's just so stressful. This has been
OL,14,Fgoing on since Sunday now. We haven't
OL,15,Fhad a clue what's going on, no one can
OL,16,Fgive us a straight answer about when
OL,17,Fwe can open, and when the water is
OL,18,Fgoing to be back on.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@JO]
