OL,3,CHouseholds left without water as
OL,4,Cdemand soars in hot weather
OL,6,F"The staff are in limbo. We've lost
OL,7,Fhundreds of pounds worth of stock and
OL,8,Fthousands of pounds worth of takings
OL,9,Feveryday. We've got accommodation here
OL,10,Ftoo and the poor people in the
OL,11,Fglamping pods have been complaining
OL,12,Feveryday. We have taken them bottled
OL,13,Fwater but it's not enough for them to
OL,14,Fhave showers.
OL,16,F"It's not what you expect at this time
OL,17,Fof year. It's hot - we need the water.
OL,18,FWe cannot function as a pub without
OL,19,Fthe water.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
