OL,3,CHouseholds left without water as
OL,4,Cdemand soars in hot weather
OL,6,F"It's incredibly frustrating and not
OL,7,Fwhat we need at this time of year."
OL,9,FA spokesperson for SWW confirmed a
OL,10,Ftanker is in place to boost supplies
OL,11,Fin the area where the Travellers Rest
OL,12,Fis located.
